snippet.title: Super Tofu Friends Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Super Tofu Friends is a running platformer where you play as a happy platonic solid going about its day. Jump, stretch, and squash to avoid obstacles such as sugary treats and the crushing emptiness of the void. As we all do.

Available for free on itch.io: https://nightshiftstudios.itch.io/super-tofu-friends
Follow us on twitter here: https://twitter.com/pitney10000

Music by Jeff Kurtenacker
http://www.jeffkurtenacker.com
https://www.youtube.com/user/jeffkurtenacker
